&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we are&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Picnic, we’re reinventing the way employees experience lunch at work. By partnering with top local restaurants and batching hundreds of orders, we make it easy for companies to offer high-quality, individually packed meals, without fees or tips. Our mission is to create a seamless, affordable, and joyful lunch experience that benefits both employees and employers.&lt;/p&gt;
