&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re hiring a City Operations Associate to support Picnic&#39;s expansion. This is a dynamic and hands-on role ideal for someone early in their career who loves logistics and metrics. If you&#39;re ready to dive in and build the foundational skills for a career in supply chain and operations, this is your chance!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This position follows a Wednesday–Sunday schedule. Working on weekends is a core and non-negotiable part of the role&lt;/strong&gt; — our operation runs at full speed on Saturdays and Sundays, and we need someone who&#39;s ready to show up and own it. Monday is your day off.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is where the rubber meets the road. You won&#39;t just be watching; you&#39;ll be actively maintaining the systems that power our operation, giving you a crash course in high-growth logistics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be the Data Dynamo:&lt;/strong&gt; You&#39;ll be the guardian of our operational data, ensuring it&#39;s clean, accurate, and actionable. This means you&#39;ll learn the crucial link between data integrity and real-world delivery success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Master Quality Assurance:&lt;/strong&gt; Sharpen your eye for detail by running essential quality checks and data audits. You&#39;ll proactively spot issues and keep our operations sharp, learning best practices in operational efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Solve Real-World Roadblocks:&lt;/strong&gt; Step up as the go-to problem solver for complex, process-driven requests. You&#39;ll manage critical tasks—from payment processing issues to necessary regulatory applications (alcohol, tobacco, health permits)—directly enabling our core Operations team to focus on daily execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;System Trainer &amp;amp; Supporter:&lt;/strong&gt; Empower your colleagues by becoming an expert on our internal systems and tools. You&#39;ll train new users and provide professional, friendly support via phone and email, developing crucial communication and leadership skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Embrace the Start-up Hustle:&lt;/strong&gt; No two days will be the same! You&#39;ll jump in on diverse Business Operations projects whenever needed, giving you exposure to different facets of a fast-growing tech company and letting you discover where your next career move could be.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we&#39;re looking for&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You don&#39;t need years of experience; we&#39;re looking for raw potential, a passion for getting things done, and a mindset ready to learn and grow!&lt;/p&gt;
