&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join Picnic as a Delivery Driver!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Picnic, we’re reinventing the way employees experience lunch at work. By partnering with top local restaurants and batching hundreds of orders, we make it easy for companies to offer high-quality, individually packed meals, without fees or tips. Our mission is to create a seamless, affordable, and joyful lunch experience that benefits both employees and employers.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ready to thrive in our dynamic environment? As a Delivery Driver you will organize, pick-up, and transport food orders with accurate scanning and smart handoffs to our Tower Ambassadors.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Create a community bridge between Picnic and eaters.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
