&lt;p&gt;Ability to lift up to 30 pounds and navigate stairs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Have a reliable source of transportation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;iPhone or Android Smartphone&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;License &amp;amp; Insurance: Valid driver’s license, clean driving record, and insurance.*&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;*Scooter drivers are exempt&lt;/p&gt;
