&lt;p&gt;Proficiency in English needed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Positive attitude in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous experience in food service or delivery app drivers are usually a good fit.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
