&lt;li&gt;Own deals from first meeting through close and beyond: discovery, pitch, proposal, signature, and beyond to onboarding, ensuring a great first picnic lunch.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with SDRs on territory prioritization and help shape outreach targeting based on your on-the-ground knowledge of the market&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run a consultative sales process: understand what each company needs and show them how Picnic fits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
