&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a data-driven, results-oriented &lt;strong&gt;Growth Marketing Specialist&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to lead the strategy, execution, and optimization of integrated demand generation programs that drive pipeline growth and revenue. This role owns the full-funnel demand engine, from awareness and lead acquisition through MQL generation, pipeline creation, and revenue attribution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate combines strong digital marketing expertise with a deep understanding of marketing operations, lead management, conversion optimization, and performance measurement. They are equally comfortable building campaign strategy, managing paid acquisition programs, optimizing nurture journeys, and analyzing attribution data to identify growth opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Demand Generation Strategy &amp;amp; Execution&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute integrated demand generation programs that drive qualified pipeline and revenue growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own demand generation plans aligned to company growth objectives and sales targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and manage multi-channel campaigns across paid media, webinars, virtual events, email marketing, content syndication, organic channels, and partner marketing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously optimize conversion rates throughout the buyer journey using testing, segmentation, and audience insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Paid Digital Marketing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage paid acquisition programs across channels including Google Ads, LinkedIn, display, retargeting, and emerging digital platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee budget allocation, bid strategies, audience targeting, and campaign performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze channel efficiency and optimize CAC, CPL, MQL volume, pipeline contribution, and ROI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with content and creative teams to develop compelling campaign assets and messaging.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Webinar &amp;amp; Virtual Event Programs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the strategy and execution of webinar and virtual event programs designed to generate pipeline and accelerate opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with internal subject matter experts, partners, and external speakers to develop engaging event content.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish event KPIs, attendee engagement strategies, follow-up workflows, and post-event reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Measure event impact on MQLs, pipeline generation, opportunity progression, and revenue influence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead Management &amp;amp; Marketing Operations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Sales and Marketing Operations to define and optimize lead lifecycle stages, including MQL, SQL, and opportunity definitions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage lead scoring frameworks, qualification criteria, routing rules, and nurturing programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor funnel performance and identify opportunities to improve lead quality, conversion rates, and sales alignment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure data quality, segmentation accuracy, and campaign tracking integrity across marketing syst

