&lt;p data-start=&quot;209&quot; data-end=&quot;255&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;209&quot; data-end=&quot;255&quot;&gt;Los Angeles, CA (In-Office, 5 Days a Week)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;257&quot; data-end=&quot;274&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;260&quot; data-end=&quot;274&quot;&gt;Who We Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;276&quot; data-end=&quot;558&quot;&gt;At Picnic, we’re building the next generation of food halls—modern, high-traffic spaces that help restaurants grow, expand, and reach new customers. Our mission is to empower restaurateurs with the space, tools, and on-site experience needed to thrive in a delivery-first world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;560&quot; data-end=&quot;616&quot;&gt;Learn more at &lt;strong data-start=&quot;574&quot; data-end=&quot;615&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Picnic&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;618&quot; data-end=&quot;639&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;621&quot; data-end=&quot;639&quot;&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;641&quot; data-end=&quot;943&quot;&gt;As a &lt;strong data-start=&quot;646&quot; data-end=&quot;663&quot;&gt;GTM Recruiter&lt;/strong&gt;, you will be responsible for scaling the customer-facing teams that power Picnic’s growth. You’ll hire high-performing talent across Sales, Marketing, Account Management, and Operations—bringing in the operators and storytellers who drive revenue, occupancy, and partner success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;945&quot; data-end=&quot;954&quot;&gt;You will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;956&quot; data-end=&quot;1511&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;956&quot; data-end=&quot;1046&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;958&quot; data-end=&quot;1046&quot;&gt;Own the full-cycle recruiting process for GTM roles across multiple teams and markets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1047&quot; data-end=&quot;1191&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1049&quot; data-end=&quot;1191&quot;&gt;Partner closely with GTM leaders to define ideal candidate profiles, refine hiring plans, and align recruiting strategy with business goals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1192&quot; data-end=&quot;1317&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1194&quot; data-end=&quot;1317&quot;&gt;Build and maintain high-quality pipelines through targeted sourcing, outbound engagement, and competitive market mapping.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1318&quot; data-end=&quot;1421&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1320&quot; data-end=&quot;1421&quot;&gt;Use data to assess funnel performance, identify bottlenecks, and continuously raise the hiring bar.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1422&quot; data-end=&quot;1511&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1424&quot; data-end=&quot;1511&quot;&gt;Represent Picnic’s mission and value proposition with clarity, energy, and credibility.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
