&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we are&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Picnic, we’re reinventing the way employees experience lunch at work. By partnering with top local restaurants and batching hundreds of orders, we make it easy for companies to offer high-quality, individually packed meals, without fees or tips. Our mission is to create a seamless, affordable, and joyful lunch experience that benefits both employees and employers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Inbound Lead Management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are the first line of communication for prospects who are interested in Picnic. You will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to inbound leads as they come in, in a timely manner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Qualify leads for AEs to ensure only relevant opportunities enter our AEs’ pipelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the lead pipeline in Salesforce, ensuring staging and notes are accurate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handoff qualified leads to AEs with notes and suggestions to help move the deal through the pipeline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Top-of-Funnel Pipeline Creation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will create qualified sales opportunities for U.S.-based Account Executives and Growth Leads.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build targeted account lists across priority U.S. markets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify companies that fit Picnic’s ideal customer profile: office-based teams, meaningful employee density, no cafeteria, and a strong need for daily individual lunch.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Find and verify relevant decision-makers, including Office Managers, Workplace Experience leaders, People / HR leaders, Facilities leaders, Executive Assistants, and Operations leaders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run outbound across email, phone, LinkedIn, referrals, and other channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cold call prospects and qualify interest in real time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Book qualified meetings directly for U.S.-based AEs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain clean CRM hygiene and structured notes so AEs can take meetings with full context.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Campaign Execution and Experimentation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Launch outbound campaigns by city, vertical, building, company size, buyer persona, and use case.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Test messaging around employee lunch benefits, office attendance, workplace experience, no-fee /no-tip delivery, funded lunch programs, and replacing fragmented DoorDash / Uber Eats behavior.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use AI tools to personalize outreach at scale without making it feel automated.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track which messages, personas, cities, and channels produce the highest-quality meetings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Share learnings with AEs and leadership so the broader team gets smarter every week.&lt;/li&gt;
